{
    "text": "\ud83c\udff0 \ud835\udc02\ud835\udc0e\ud835\udc0b\ud835\udc0e\ud835\udc0c\ud835\udc00\ud835\udc11\ud835\udc04\ud835\udc12 \ud83c\uddea\ud83c\uddf8  \ud83c\uddeb\ud83c\uddf7 Situ\u00e9 \u00e0 Benalmadena (Sud de l'Espagne), ce ch\u00e2teau a \u00e9t\u00e9 construit \u00e0 la fin du XX\u00e8me si\u00e8cle par le docteur Esteban Mart\u00edn, accompagn\u00e9 de deux ma\u00e7ons.  En utilisant plusieurs mat\u00e9riaux tels que la pierre, la brique ou encore le bois, le monument nous raconte l'histoire de la d\u00e9couverte du continent am\u00e9ricain \u00e0 travers diff\u00e9rentes sc\u00e8nes.  Un hommage \u00e0 Christophe Colomb.  Qu\u2019en pensez-vous? \ud83e\uddd0  \ud83c\uddec\ud83c\udde7 Located in Benalmadena (South of Spain), this castle was built at the end of the 20th century by Doctor Esteban Mart\u00edn, accompanied by two masons.  Using several materials such as stone, brick or even wood, the monument tells us the story of the discovery of the American continent through different scenes.  A tribute to Christopher Columbus.  What do you think about it ? \ud83e\uddd0  \ud83d\udcf8 @rutaideal \ud83d\udc4c . #colomares #europeancastles #castlesofeurope #chateaux #ch\u00e2teaux #christophecolomb #christophercolumbus #castlesofinstagram #espagne\ud83c\uddea\ud83c\uddf8 #spaintourism #spaintoday #castle #castles #patrimoine #benalmadena #costadelsol",
